# features
- Chesterfield
- help and rules descriptions
- menu scrollable with the mouse wheel
- labels for the menus

# known bugs
- undo doesn't work correct with 
	* klondike 3
	* spider 124
- if you open a dialog through the context menu, edje seems to be frozen.
  This is probably a EWL bug. A work around at the moment is to open
  and close the context menu with a right click.
- the card theme selector seems not to show all installed themes  
